# run_20260430_170325: Phase 2 sanity train, combo A (une_merge_v1_nosides + split_v2 + dropunk), 80ep. S4 best (top macro 0.747, acc 0.770, top-2 0.940, min 0.403). Collapse-rescue confirmed on Phase-2 data: +0.058 min vs combo B; essentially tied with Phase-1 collapsed-classes baseline.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260430_170325/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_4.pt

# run_20260430_213933: Phase 2 LS sweep cell 1, combo A nosides + LS=0.0, 80ep. S2 best (top min 0.404). Hypothesis (LS=0.0 lifts wrist_smash) not supported: vs LS=0.1 baseline run_20260430_170325, head metrics flat, mean wrist_smash -1.6 pp, best-of-run wrist_smash -5.5 pp.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260430_213933/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260501_073430: Phase 2 LS sweep cell 2, combo A nosides + LS=0.15, 80ep. S3 best (top macro 0.753, top min 0.448, top acc 0.773). Vs LS=0.1 baseline run_20260430_170325, head metrics flat (+0.005 macro mean), mean wrist_smash +4.2 pp, range tightens 0.159 -> 0.066.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_073430/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_3.pt

# run_20260501_110525: Phase 2 class-weighting smoke test, combo A nosides + LS=0.15 + class_weights={wrist_smash:2.0, smash:2.0}, 80ep. S2 best (top min 0.518) — NEW PROJECT-WIDE CEILING on wrist_smash F1 (prior best 0.46 LS=0.1 S5; first nosides serial to clear 0.50). S4 of same run also sets new ceilings: macro 0.756, acc 0.777, drive 0.66. Mean shift vs LS=0.15 alone is flat (+0.001/+0.005/+0.001/-0.002); the lift is bimodal across seeds, not central-tendency.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_110525/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260501_164658: Phase 2 CDB-F1 first cell, combo A nosides + LS=0.0 + adaptive_focal{tau=1, gamma=1, momentum=0.9, warm_up=5, f1_floor=0}, 80ep. S2 best (top min 0.486, top macro 0.753, top acc 0.769, top top-2 0.940). Mean ws +4.0 pp on class-weighted (largest single-run floor lift on the loss side so far); push +6.7 pp (adaptive picked up push as a bottleneck the static config missed). Cost: smash -5.5 pp (pair-confusion residual). Ws range tightens to 0.413-0.486 (vs class-weighted 0.378-0.518); bimodal-seed problem solved. Project ceiling not broken: S2 0.486 < class-weighted S2 0.518.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_164658/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260501_192113: CDB-F1 follow-up, combo A nosides + adaptive_focal{tau=1, gamma=0, momentum=0.9, warm_up=5, f1_floor=0}, 80ep, bourbaki. Same as the first CDB-F1 run (run_20260501_164658) with gamma flipped to 0. S1 best (top min 0.494, only seed clearing 0.49; macro 0.743, acc 0.758). Vs the first run mean: macro -0.3, min -2.8, acc -0.3, top-2 +0.0. Macro didn't move and ws dropped 2.8 pp, so gamma=1 was where the bottleneck lift came from. Smash +2.5, drive +2.5 picked up.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_192113/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides.pt

# run_20260501_192519: CDB-F1 follow-up, combo A nosides + adaptive_focal{tau=0.5, gamma=1, momentum=0.9, warm_up=5, f1_floor=0}, 80ep, engelbart. Same as the first CDB-F1 run (run_20260501_164658) with tau softened to 0.5. S2 best by head metrics (top macro 0.753, top acc 0.772, top-2 0.940), despite run-low ws 0.367; top-of-run ws on S5 (0.447). Vs the first run mean: macro +0.2, min -5.0, acc +0.5, top-2 +0.4. Wrist_smash gain gone; smash +2.3, drive +2.8, passive_drop +1.1, rush +1.1 picked up. With run_20260501_192113, both tau and gamma had to be that aggressive in the first run; pair-cap on smash next.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_192519/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260501_230252: Pair-cap CDB-F1 run, combo A nosides + adaptive_focal{tau=1, gamma=1, momentum=0.9, warm_up=5, f1_floor=0, pair_caps=[{numer:smash, denom:wrist_smash, ratio:0.7}]}, 80ep, bourbaki. Same config as the first CDB-F1 run (run_20260501_164658) plus a pair-cap rule on smash<->ws. S4 best by head metrics (top macro 0.748, top acc 0.767, top-2 0.933, ws 0.418). Vs the first CDB-F1 run mean: macro -0.3, min -5.2, acc -0.1, top-2 -0.1. Cap didn't land: smash +1.2 pp but ws gave back 5.2 pp. Predicted band was smash +2-4 with ws holding within ~1; both halves missed. Macro flat because the trade cancelled at the head. Next: ratio sweep or Seesaw-F1.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260501_230252/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_4.pt

# run_20260502_075808: Gamma=2 follow-up, combo A nosides + adaptive_focal{tau=1, gamma=2, momentum=0.9, warm_up=5, f1_floor=0}, 80ep, bourbaki. Single-knob change vs the first CDB-F1 run (run_20260501_164658): gamma 1 -> 2 (focal literature default). S3 best by ws (0.4873, run-high, on a par with the first CDB-F1 S2's 0.4863). Macro 0.7330 / acc 0.7494 bottom-half of run. Vs the first CDB-F1 run mean: macro -0.7, min -4.1, acc -0.6, top-2 -0.1. Gamma=2 didn't lift the floor; aggressive per-example modulator over-discounts moderate-confidence ws examples. Last untouched CDB knob, now tested.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260502_075808/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_3.pt

# run_20260503_104300: Capacity bump Run 1, mlp_head hidden 400 -> 1200 via head_dim * mlp_d_scale swap on bst.py:199, encoder untouched. y1t1 hparams otherwise (combo A nosides + LS=0.0 + adaptive_focal{tau=1, gamma=1}), 80ep, bourbaki. S1 best by ws (0.4449). Mean macro 0.7414 / min 0.4138 / acc 0.7604 / top-2 0.9320. Vs y1t1 mean (run_20260501_164658): macro -0.2, min -4.8, acc -0.1, top-2 -0.3. Head metrics flat, ws cost 4.8 pp.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260503_104300/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides.pt

# run_20260503_172922: Shuttle-unzeroing-on-keypoint-fail run, branch shuttle/wipe-drop, ablation_id=wipe_drop (only train-loop signal of the data change). Drops shuttle[failed,:] = 0 at prepare_train_on_shuttleset.py:866-867 (~14k frames). Hparams otherwise identical to the first CDB-F1 run (run_20260501_164658). S2 best (top macro 0.756, top acc 0.768 tied S4, min 0.494). Mean 0.7481/0.4742/0.7653/0.9353. Vs first CDB-F1 mean: macro +0.5, min +1.2, acc +0.4, top-2 flat. Smash +1.5% / ws +1.2%: first time the pair moved up together.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260503_172922/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260503_192718: Shuttle-mask run, branch shuttle/mask-wiring, ablation_id=mask_wiring (only train-loop signal of the data + model change). Carries the shuttle-unzeroing change plus a variant 2a shuttle_missing channel fused post-TCN (mask_proj Linear(1,4) + shuttle_fuse Linear(d_model+4, d_model)). Hparams otherwise identical to the shuttle-unzeroing run (run_20260503_172922). S4 best (top min 0.490, top top-2 0.939, top ws, top pair-sum 1.085). Mean 0.7440/0.4568/0.7630/0.9365. Vs shuttle-unzeroing mean: macro -0.4, min -1.7, acc -0.2, top-2 +0.1. Mask did not lift over unzeroing alone (model already inferred missing-shuttle from xy + temporal context). Branch parked; design captured in scratch/architecture_notes/.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260503_192718/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_4.pt

# run_20260504_152529: Jitter-off ablation, RandomTranslation_batch(prob=0.0) at bst_train.py:375; otherwise identical to wipe_drop best (run_20260503_172922). S2 best (top min 0.485, top pair-sum 1.225). Mean 0.7401/0.4301/0.7586/0.9365. Vs wipe_drop: macro -0.8, min -4.4, acc -0.7, top-2 +0.1. Wrist_smash mean 0.4742 -> 0.4301; S4/S5 min F1 floor at 0.39 / 0.36. Min F1 ends up below the first CDB-F1 baseline too: the broken bbox-centric jitter was empirically regularising. Defaults restored.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260504_152529/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_2.pt

# run_20260505_111211: Augmentation framework v1, branch aug-framework-v1. Coupled centreline flip (p_flip=0.5) + pos+shuttle constrained jitter (cap_y=0.05, cap_x=0.10, eps=0.15, p_jitter=0.2). Replaces the broken joints-only RandomTranslation_batch with the corrected multi-stream coupled formulation. Hparams otherwise identical to the wipe_drop best (run_20260503_172922). S5 best (top min 0.503, smash 0.503 / ws 0.518: first project serial where smash takes over as the floor class). Mean 0.7388/0.4750/0.7591/0.9402. Vs wipe_drop: macro -0.9, min flat, acc -0.6, top-2 +0.5. Cross_court_net_shot -5.7% (largest single-class movement), smash -3.0%, push -2.1%; ws +0.4%, drive +1.6%.
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260505_111211/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_5.pt

# run_20260505_154907: Aug framework v1, p_jitter 0.2 -> 0.3 (under-reg test). Hparams otherwise identical to the previous aug run (run_20260505_111211). S5 best (top min 0.515 project high, smash 0.515 / ws 0.519: smash again the floor class, pair sum 1.033). Mean 0.7447/0.4779/0.7635/0.9394. Vs prev aug run: macro +0.6, min +0.3, acc +0.4, top-2 ~flat. Vs wipe_drop best: macro -0.3, min +0.4, acc -0.2, top-2 +0.4. Aug now at parity-or-better than wipe_drop on the head metrics, ahead on floor and top-2. Rush +2.6%, drive +2.6% picked up; cross_court_net_shot -5.4% persists (not on the exposure axis; flip ablation flagged).
!main_on_shuttleset/experiments/run_20260505_154907/weights/bst_CG_AP_JnB_bone_between_2_hits_with_max_limits_seq_100_une_merge_v1_nosides_5.pt
